# Agents

This file is a sibling to `CLAUDE.md` and applies the same per-branch guidance
to any AI tool that reads `AGENTS.md` (Codex, Cursor, etc.). The authoritative
content for this branch lives in `CLAUDE.md` — read it first.

build-branches.sh copies `CLAUDE.md.<branch>` to both `CLAUDE.md` and
`AGENTS.md` on each branch, so the two stay in sync.
